    "spell_level": "bard 3, cleric/oracle 3, druid 4, paladin 3, sorcerer/wizard 3, summoner/unchained summoner 3, witch 3, inquisitor 3, antipaladin 3, magus 3, shaman 3, occultist 3, psychic 3, mesmerist 3, spiritualist 3, medium 3",
